        "introduction": [
            {
                "titre": "This budget friendly \"hack\" is more than just being frugal ..or cheap for the sake of saving money (or stretching a dollar), this \"home remedy\" also helps when you don't quite like all ingredients in store-bought lotions (or soaps, shampoos, conditioners) -this tip gives you ideas on putting some good stuff in them and getting more outof them.",
                "sous_items": []
            },
            {
                "titre": "For anyone who has put water in your lotion (or soaps, shampoos, conditioners), and turned them into \"THIN\" potion- this is for you! Either bargain brand or name brand products will work (..neither one will like it :). So be sure to use a watered-down lotion or conditioner! The idea is to THICKEN it AND SHARE IT.",
                "sous_items": []
            }
        ],
